title: Ty Segall - Discography
description:
This is my collection of Studio Albums released by/as Ty Segall. I've also added

Fuzz, the self titled LP from Fuzz (the band in which Ty Segall drums). And Hair, 

the LP by Ty and White Fence. This collection is not complete, I'm missing Ty 

Segall's self titled LP, released in 2008.




The bit rate for these albums are as high as possible, I couldn't find any better

versions. The bit rate doesn't distract listening anyway, if anything it enhances the 

rawness of the recording.



STUDIO LP'S (as Ty Segall)


Horn the Unicorn (192kbps)(2008)

Lemons (200kbps approx)(VBR)(2009

Melted (250kbps approx)(VBR)(2010)

Goodbye Bread (250kbps approx)(VBR)(2011)

Slaughterhouse (320kbps)(2012)

Twins (320kbps)(2012)

Sleeper (320kbps)(2013)


OTHER ALBUMS

Fuzz - Fuzz (320kbps)(2013)

Hair - Ty Segall & White Fence (320kbps)(2012)
